<span class="postbody">My general pollicy (especially since I often group with others I dont know) need before greed is great.  However if your charicter cannot use it, goes on lotto.  Otherwise anyone could make up oh my alt needs this and that, and just go sell the crap.  I have grouped with some very good people and of course they earned a break, but every once in a while you get thoes cheaty dishonest people you really have to watch out for.  So I say if he wants it for his alt, let him play his alt and loot it for himself.  Sorry to sound cold but there is no reason one person deserves more because he has alot of alts.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
