<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">This has been discussed to death during EQ1 but NBG only works when everyone is honest. However, there are enough people who try to cheat the system that it doesn't work. I've taken to going in on all loot because every pickup group I've been in has been this way. Even when someone has won something they still go in on other loot. I've seen groups where one guy has made out with 3 or 4 pieces of loot while there are still people who hasn't even won one. So I've taken to going in on all loot, giving it to friends if I don't need it and selling whatever else is there. I wish I didn't have to do this but it's either that or watch everyone else do it and then have to buy my stuff off of those everyone else. It's why I prefer a guild group or with friends.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
